From cc16c451c0560c9484c8530caa167af71c77bc67 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Benjamin A. Beasley" <code@musicinmybrain.net>
Date: Wed, 13 Sep 2023 07:40:41 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Remove shebang from urlpy.py
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

In addition to not having the executable bit set, this is an importable
module and has no “main routine” or interesting side effects.

Signed-off-by: Benjamin A. Beasley <code@musicinmybrain.net>
---
 urlpy.py | 2 --
 1 file changed, 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/urlpy.py b/urlpy.py
index 95c500c..c3f2136 100644
--- a/urlpy.py
+++ b/urlpy.py
@@ -1,5 +1,3 @@
-#!/usr/bin/env python
-#
 # Copyright (c) nexB, Inc.
 # Copyright (c) 2012-2015 SEOmoz, Inc.
 #

From bcaadd7f978861d7e45b41a8ccf5eabec5ae6755 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Benjamin A. Beasley" <code@musicinmybrain.net>
Date: Wed, 13 Sep 2023 07:42:03 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Remove shebang from setup.py

While this file is script-like, it does not have the executable bit set,
so the shebang line is not useful.

Signed-off-by: Benjamin A. Beasley <code@musicinmybrain.net>
---
 setup.py | 2 --
 1 file changed, 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/setup.py b/setup.py
index 18c9487..8d85550 100644
--- a/setup.py
+++ b/setup.py
@@ -1,5 +1,3 @@
-#!/usr/bin/env python
-
 # Copyright (c) nexB, Inc.
 # Copyright (c) 2012-2015 SEOmoz, Inc.
 #
